import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import '../node_modules/bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import {BrowserRouter} from 'react-router-dom'


ReactDOM.render(
  <>
  <BrowserRouter>
<App/>
</BrowserRouter>
</>,
document.getElementById('root'))
